{"tid":569688,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[支爆港樓一定死]【安邦出事】安邦旗下投資多隻港股 重倉民行、招行","createTime":"2018-02-23T02:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T15:21:14.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1f31319e3746c85b8a24332d4dcc87889eafc27a","tid":569688,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:35:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180223/57864750\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180223%2F57864750&d=46fcM0%2BWrLG%2F%2F9vNxla2UGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=33f71f36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180223%2F57864750&h=418cc2b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180223/57864750</a><br />\n<br />\n自安邦集團董事長吳小暉去年6月被當局有關部門帶走後，有指中保監已派工作組進駐安邦，今日更宣佈依然正式接管安邦。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">安邦</span>資產逾萬億元，旗下基金、保險及養老基金<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">持有眾多港股。</span><br />\n<br />\n截至去年中，安邦持有港股包括招行（３９６８）約10%，持民行（1988）約15%，持萬科（2202）約5%，持遠洋（3377）約30%，持金風科技（2208）約8.7%，持晨鳴紙業（1812）約1.5%。另外亦持有中交建（1800）、中鐵（390）、中鐵建（1186）、大唐環境（1272）等等。<br />\n而自安邦去年6月出事後，已大手減持內銀A股，套現66億元，其減持股份包括持工行3.9億股、中行3.3億股、建行1.3億股，以及農行8.81億股。"},{"pid":"958c43f1f05effbbd858eddde13f5fdd281cf7bb","tid":569688,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:37:03.000Z","msg":"冇錯，雷sir英明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abd620177348a65251a1aa9bc946fc9aa0ceea3","tid":569688,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"958c43f1f05effbbd858eddde13f5fdd281cf7bb","tid":569688,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:37:03.000Z","msg":"冇錯，雷sir英明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-